cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object and part localization in images for fine-grained recognition. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a nonparametric data-driven method for object and part localization. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with recognition of sub-ordinate categories in images. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image recognition and feature extraction. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper involves retrieval of similar images from the training set for annotation transfer.
